236
00:16:39,615 --> 00:16:40,915
<i>Sugestões?</i>

237
00:16:41,617 --> 00:16:43,934
Algumas destas
são bem boas.

238
00:17:04,073 --> 00:17:05,373
Cristo.

239
00:17:08,444 --> 00:17:09,845
<i>Cara.</i>

240
00:17:09,846 --> 00:17:13,281
Conversando, cumprimentando,
entregando panfletos.

241
